criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Volunteer women above 18 years old with histological confirmed breast cancer in stages
        I-IIIA who have finished their treatment, such as surgery, chemotherapy and radiotherapy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiovascular disease (except hypertension controlled by medication);

          -  Metastatic disease or active regional locus;

          -  Physical or psychiatric impairments for exercise;

          -  Severe nausea;

          -  Anorexia;

          -  Participation in exercise more than 75 minutes/week
